# 0.0.3 - 10/30/2024
- Add confirmation pop up box "Verification Started".
    - Maybe change later, for a "confirmation state", with button change.
- Add packages for `{confirm, message}`, imports in `Cargo.lock`, `Cargo.toml` & `tauri.conf.json`.
- Add 'rem' patterns to `App.css`.
    - Change 'pixels' sizes to 'rems'.
- Add `useState` to `App.tsx`
    - Add consts `selectedCount`, `setSelectedCount` & `updateSelectedCount`.
- Rename `settings-container` to `container_settings` in `App.tsx`.
- Rename `integrations_main` to `container_integrations` in `App.tsx`.
- Rename `integrationsSelected` to `selectedCount` in `integrations_header.tsx`.
- Add `IntegrationsListProps` interface & `updateSelectedCount` in `integrations_listing.tsx`.
- Add `invoke`, `confirm` & `message` imports & `updateSelectedCount` in `integrations_pattern.tsx`.
- Remove  `isDisabled`, `onEnableAction` & `onDisableAction` from `integrations_pattern.tsx`.
- Fix `handleCheckboxChange`, `handleVerifyClick` & return class names in `integrations_pattern.tsx`.
- Remove `Interface` option from list in `settings_sidebar.tsx`.

### Started implementation of repos verification for new version & actuall integration download.

# 0.0.2 - 10/16/2024
### App Changes
- Renamed "extension(s)" files, to "integration(s)".
- Added button effects & main color pattern on `App.css` as `.integration-item button`

### Notes
- No actual installation has been added, since i rather implement a verification for each integration that is added, before making it available. But i decided to publish the interface done so far, to show that the project is not abandoned/deprecated.


